{"id":255550,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-刘晓原、王仲夏今日举牌强烈要求无罪释/","date":"2012-10-08T15:31:27Z","modified":"2012-10-08T15:31:27Z","title":"维权网 | 刘晓原、王仲夏今日举牌强烈要求无罪释放朱承志（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>（维权网信息员赵小明报道）著名维权律师刘晓原、维权人士王仲夏今日（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日星期一）举牌强烈要求当局立即无罪释放朱承志。对于朱承志案，刘晓原律师一直予以强烈关注，日前他在网上呼吁网民为朱承志祝贺生日表达支持。今天他又和维权人士王仲夏一起举牌表达关注。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘晓原表示：“朱承志原是一个访民，在个体维权过程中，开始介入社会事件。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">09</span><span>年时，因为在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>国新办</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>外拍摄访民照片，被北京警方刑拘一个月，当时我担任他的律师，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>幸运</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>的是后被警方以无罪释放。逃脱了牢狱之灾。如今，他成了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>政治犯</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>，不知能否再次逃脱牢狱之灾？”刘晓原还认为：“因为关注一个老人（李旺阳）之死，竟然还会遭到涉嫌煽颠犯罪指控，实在是很荒唐。</span>”<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3sIJCjfcMGA/UHLr1l4txzI/AAAAAAAAQzI/7Zyy1xjzxk4/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"220\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3sIJCjfcMGA/UHLr1l4txzI/AAAAAAAAQzI/7Zyy1xjzxk4/s400/2.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1y13ekSpRoc/UHLr2htLb6I/AAAAAAAAQzQ/ZzzP1NhKtKQ/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"231\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1y13ekSpRoc/UHLr2htLb6I/AAAAAAAAQzQ/ZzzP1NhKtKQ/s400/1.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1865696466876991375?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigita